data.text:
2019

Drama

Watchlist

Where to Watch

Writer-director Rupam Sarmah's drama features over eighty actors with real disabilities. It follows an American neurologist who travels to India to study music therapy and finds herself in a position to empower the disabled children and adults in her newfound community through the power of music.
